{"data":{"id":"49563817","title":"SASS\\SCSS \u907f\u514d\u8fd0\u7b97\u7684\u65b9\u6cd5","articleedittype":1,"description":"\u4eca\u5929\u7528sass\u5199\u4e00\u4e2a\u6837\u5f0f\uff0c\u6587\u5b57\u63cf\u8fb9\u3002\u56e0\u4e3a\u5176\u4ee3\u7801\u6bd4\u8f83\u957f\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u5c31\u7528@mixin \u6df7\u5165\u3002\u4f46\u662f\u53d1\u73b0\uff0c\u6211\u8fd9\u6837\u5199\u6709\u95ee\u9898\u3002\u53d1\u751f\u4e86\u6211\u4e0d\u60f3\u8981\u7684sass\u8fd0\u7b97\uff0c\u600e\u4e48\u89e3\u51b3\u5462\uff1f","content":"<p>\u4eca\u5929\u7528<code>sass<\/code>\u5199\u4e00\u4e2a\u6837\u5f0f\uff0c\u6587\u5b57\u63cf\u8fb9\u3002\u56e0\u4e3a\u5176\u4ee3\u7801\u6bd4\u8f83\u957f\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u5c31\u7528@mixin \u6df7\u5165\u3002\u4f46\u662f\u53d1\u73b0\uff0c\u6211\u8fd9\u6837\u5199\u6709\u95ee\u9898\u3002<\/p>\n\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code class=\" hljs mel\"><span class=\"hljs-variable\">@mixin<\/span> ts(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">1<\/span>px,<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s2<\/span>:<span class=\"hljs-number\">1<\/span>px,<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$color<\/span>:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cff<\/span>){\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">text<\/span>-shadow:\n    <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s2<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$color<\/span>,\n    -<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s2<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$color<\/span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> -<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s2<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$color<\/span>,\n    -<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> -<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s1<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$s2<\/span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$color<\/span>;\n}<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>\u8fd9\u6837\u8f93\u51fa\u7684\u4ee3\u7801\uff0